Package: blblm
Type: Package
Title: Bag of Little Bootstraps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Vishnu", "Rangiah", email = "vrrangiah@ucdavis.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <vrrangiah@ucdavis.edu>
Description: blblm is used to implement the bag of little bootstraps for the linear regression model. 
    It also includes implementation for the bag for the random forest (e.g. blbrf) and logistic regression models (e.g. blblogreg).
    For bigger datasets and for greater efficiency the package can implement the functions in parallel computing when using the parameter (parallel = TRUE).
